[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（その手紙が来たのは、無数島群域への航海に向けて\n　準備をしていた頃のことだった）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "あれ、手紙だ。珍し。差出人は……カロリン？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "久しぶりだな。教会を出てからも、\nたまに私書箱でやりとりしてたけど……なになに……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "……は？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "システム",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "“ユンゲルス家のことで、お話があります”",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 965274698
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "そっか。ヨハナも行けなくなったのか～",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "4318551206560057077",
		"text": "「も」ってことは……あんたも？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "125453364659396444",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "まー、元の家族とちょっとね。\nなんかややこしいことになってるみたいでさ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "ほったらかしにしたまま、\n逃げるわけにもいかないっていうか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "4979147540429202173",
		"text": "ハイディ、私にできることはある？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7558252374860649663",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "ははっ、大丈夫だよ相棒！\n自分でちゃんとケリをつけてくるから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "あんたは、レスナの力になってあげて",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "4979147540429202173",
		"text": "そう……分かったわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7558252374860649663",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "ま、すぐに用事が済めば、\n船出に間に合うかもしれないしね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "ヴァレリアたちはもう船出した頃かな。\n結局、間に合わなかったのは悔しいけど……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "でも、今は……あの家と向き合う時だ。\n全部決着をつけて、絶対にまたみんなと合流する！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "もう、逃げないって決めたんだ。\nみんなと前に進むために！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ユンゲルス……私が捨てた名前）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私は本当の名を、ハイディ・ユンゲルスという）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]